  <refsection id="Description_BITCLEAR">
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>
This blocks set the specified bit of the integer input to 0. The user can specify the bit in the field:"index of bit". Bit 0 is the least significant bit.  
</para>
    <para>
</para>
  </refsection>
  <refsection id="Boîtededialogue_BITCLEAR">
    <title>Boîte de dialogue</title>
    <para>
      <inlinemediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="../../../images/BITCLEAR_gui.gif" align="center" valign="middle"/>
        </imageobject>
      </inlinemediaobject>
    </para>
    <para>

</para>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <emphasis role="bold">Datatype(3=int32 4=int16 5=int8 ...)</emphasis>
        </para>
        <para> It indicates the type of the input/output data. It support all the integer datatype, number must be between 3 and 8.</para>
        <para> Propriétés : Type 'vec' de taille 1. </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <emphasis role="bold">index of bit (0 is leat significant)</emphasis>
        </para>
        <para> It indicate the index of the bit to clear. When the type is int32 or uint32 the number must be positif and less than 32. When the type is int16 or uint16 the number must be positif and less than 16. When the type is int8 or uint8 the number must be positif and less than 8.</para>
        <para> Propriétés : Type 'vec' de taille 1.</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </refsection>
